    <item>
      <title>中国德国商会称欧盟关税不会保护汽车制造商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/german-chamber-in-china-says-eu-tariffs-won-t-protect-automakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商会表示，欧盟应该投资以提高竞争力，而不是提高中国产电动汽车的关税，这为柏林方面避免或放宽贸易限制的努力提供了助力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/german-chamber-in-china-says-eu-tariffs-won-t-protect-automakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果智能功能的缓慢推出将延续到 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-16/when-is-apple-intelligence-coming-some-ai-features-won-t-arrive-until-2025-lxhjh86w</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果将​​在几个月内逐步推出新的智能功能，力求避免其他人工智能系统所面临的陷阱。此外，该公司在 Vision Pro 软件方面取得了巨大进步；新款 iPad Pro 为更薄的 iPhone 奠定了基础；与 OpenAI 的合作伙伴关系；新的卫星短信功能即将成为苹果最新的付费服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-16/when-is-apple-intelligence-coming-some-ai-features-won-t-arrive-until-2025-lxhjh86w</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 12:45:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Paytm 正与 Zomato 洽谈出售电影票务业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/paytm-said-in-talks-with-zomato-to-sell-movie-ticketing-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度金融科技先驱 Paytm 正在就将其电影和票务业务出售给 Zomato Ltd. 进行谈判，以摆脱非核心资产并重振因监管打击而受到打击的销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/paytm-said-in-talks-with-zomato-to-sell-movie-ticketing-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 07:38:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
